PrecisRe-appointment of MENOTTI IARICCI, of Montreal, Quebec, as a full-time member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Montreal Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour, for a term of four years, effective August 31, 1997.
